erd</p></a><a href="https://linkerd.io/" target="_blank" class="link-block-5 w-inline-block"><div class="text-block-79 electric">Open source Linkerd</div><p class="paragraph-48">The only service mesh that doesn&#x27;t require a team of <br/>engineers to run</p></a></div></div></nav></div><div data-hover="false" data-delay="0" class="nav-dropdown service w-dropdown"><div class="nav-link-8 w-dropdown-toggle"><a href="/service-mesh-manifesto" class="w-inline-block"><div class="text-block-64">Service Mesh</div></a></div><nav class="dropdown-list-2 servicemesh w-dropdown-list"><div class="dropdown-item-wrapper"><div class="dropdown-item first-child"><div class="dropdown-text-2">Service mesh<a href="https://buoyant.io/service-mesh-academy/"><br/></a></div><a href="/service-mesh-manifesto" class="link-block-4 w-inline-block"><div class="text-block-70 electric">The Service Mesh Manifesto</div><div class="text-block-51">What every software engineer needs to know <br/>about the service mesh.</div></a><a href="/linkerd-vs-istio" class="link-block-4 w-inline-block"><div class="text-block-71 electric">Linkerd vs Istio</div><div class="text-block-53">How do the two service meshes compare?</div></a><a href="/mtls-guide" class="link-block-4 w-inline-block"><div class="text-block-73 electric">Guide to mTLS and Kubernetes</div><div class="text-block-55">A Kubernetes engineer’s guide to mutual TLS.</div></a></div><div class="dropdown-item element_medio"><a href="/runbook/linkerd-runbook" class="link-block-col-2 runbook_menu w-inline-block"><div class="text-block-72 electric">Linkerd production runbook</div><div class="text-block-54">Buoyant&#x27;s guide to running Linkerd in production.</div></a><a href="/case-studies" class="link-block-4 cases_menu w-inline-block"><div class="text-block-74 electric">Case studies</div><div class="text-block-56">Learn how organizations across the world run Linkerd in production.</div></a></div><div id="w-node-a8287287-7c2f-f820-3494-5853eb619de8-eb619d