run.<br/><span class="text-span-7">10x lighter. 10x simpler. 100% open source.</span></h2></div><div class="div-block-9"><div id="w-node-_72a6768c-520c-100e-8dd6-b7f340ade158-2a9168cb" class="card_features"><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/625ee9b2f6a4ec3997f9c11b/6279b1f40e6604606f3b81e2_icon-zero-trust.svg" loading="lazy" width="60" alt="" class="cs_logo"/><p class="paragrpah_main">Zero trust security for any Kubernetes application</p></div><div id="w-node-ae5a1915-de91-2bff-2d4b-786ff82cb3c7-2a9168cb" class="card_features"><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/625ee9b2f6a4ec3997f9c11b/6279b1f4b337a1841683a294_icon-mutual-tls.svg" loading="lazy" width="60" alt="" class="cs_logo"/><p class="paragrpah_main">Zero-config mutual TLS for strong encryption and identity</p></div><div id="w-node-faa9ff50-3ce6-312e-820e-baba88975b6b-2a9168cb" class="card_features"><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/625ee9b2f6a4ec3997f9c11b/6279b1f4799876b416035747_icon-metrics.svg" loading="lazy" width="60" alt="" class="cs_logo"/><p class="paragrpah_main">Instant service health metrics for all HTTP and gRPC calls</p></div><div id="w-node-d9eea66c-abe4-52f2-ccf9-44676e2aa92c-2a9168cb" class="card_features"><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/625ee9b2f6a4ec3997f9c11b/6279b1f469246c4ce2b16204_icon-traffic.svg" loading="lazy" width="60" alt="" class="cs_logo"/><p class="paragrpah_main">Traffic shaping, retries, timeouts, and more</p></div><div id="w-node-_3b4c8656-69f7-d6bf-8e68-cdff9cf290e5-2a9168cb" class="card_features"><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/625ee9b2f6a4ec3997f9c11b/6279b1f47e2778b6dd5407c4_icon-secure.svg" loading="lazy" width="60" alt="" class="cs_logo"/><p class="paragrpah_main">Secure multi-cluster failover across clusters, regions, and clouds</p></div><div id="w-node-_0022d37d-ad69-5973-0984-dba8255543be-2a9168cb" class="card_features"><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/625ee9b2f6a4ec3997f9c11b/6279b1f45a5be5634c4a7e76_icon-cncf.svg"